<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太阳刚刚升起，魔法师就来到了阿拉丁的家里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一切都按我的计划在进行。”他对自己说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他焦急地用拳头敲打着门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门马上就开了，阿拉丁跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的妈妈就在他的身后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看到马格里布时，她大声说：“您好！早上好！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您好！”马格里布回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好，伯父！”阿拉丁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60010</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他鞠躬然后亲吻了马格里布的手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60011</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“玩儿得开心。”泽巴对着要出发去集市的马格里布和儿子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先，魔法师把阿拉丁带进了一个衣服店里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿出你们最好的衣服。”马格里布说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的侄子需要穿得像一个富有的商人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>商店的主人拿出了裤子，外套和背心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抛出了腰带，衬衫和鞋子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101813</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你喜欢什么就选什么。”马格里布告诉阿拉丁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101814</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想要这些裤子！这个外套！”阿拉丁大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿起几件衣服然后把它们放在手臂上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有这个！”阿拉丁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿起一顶帽子戴在自己头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像前一天一样，马格里布从他的袖子里拿出了金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他付钱给了那个商人，然后脱下了阿拉丁的帽子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你太脏了，不能戴这顶帽子，穿这些好的衣服！”马格里布说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他带着阿拉丁来到了公共浴室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洗了一个热水澡后，他们喝了果汁，一起聊了一个商人的快乐的生活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，阿拉丁穿上了他的新衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伯父，快看我！”他大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他穿着宽松的，黑色的裤子，一条很亮的腰带，和一件条纹的外套。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那顶帽子又戴到了他的头上，阿拉丁开心地跳舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一整个下午，马格里布带着阿拉丁逛了城市。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201348</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他给阿拉丁看了每个男孩儿都只能在梦里看到的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们参观了苏丹的宫殿，还有他的花园，喷泉和阳光广场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后魔法师带着阿拉丁逛了市场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“仔细看那些商人买东西，卖东西，做交易。”他对阿拉丁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会很快学会全部事情的。”阿拉丁说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很快我就会成为一个有钱人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁肚子饿了，他们去了一个小吃摊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在那里他们吃了铁板烤肉，和别的地方来的商人喝了咖啡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我的侄子，”马格里布说，“他的名字叫阿拉丁。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天黑了，阿拉丁的妈妈在门口等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿拉丁在哪里？”她心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走出了房子，看着弯曲的街道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？那个和马格里布走在一起的人是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她认不出穿着新衣服的儿子了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他已经看起来像一个有钱人了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，马格里布。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要用我剩下的日子来感谢你！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会祈祷你长寿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我希望这个男孩儿能够一直服侍你，做任何你要求的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>魔法师狡猾地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也希望如此。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他对阿拉丁说：“明天我会再来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们去逛城里的漂亮的公园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会给你看你以前从来没有看过的东西！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，阿拉丁一夜没能入睡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>